org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.metamodels.automaton

Interface InternalModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InternalModelImpl

    public interface InternalModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Internal Model'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Automata
    • Latest Event
    • Enabled For The Latest Event
    • Event Tokens In Model
    See Also:
    AutomatonPackage.getInternalModel()
